PREPARATIONS are in top gear for the UK tour of super talented singer, Shade Andrews. Beginning on June 17, 2022, Andrews will storm big cities like London, Manchester, Birmingham, Leicester, Milton Keynes, Liverpool, Glasgow, Newcastle, and Oxford to serenade fans.   Yinka Rythmz shows appreciation with new single     WurlD: I’m lucky to be accepted back in Nigeria     I’ll always be grateful to Akpabio, says Daddy Showkey   According to the Miracle Day Music signee, rhythmic and powerful songs such as Overload, Lovey Dovey, Majoo, and Shiver, among others, will take centre stage during her tour. CEO, Miracle Day Music, Omenka Uzoma Day aka Uzo said the forthcoming tour is important as Andrews has been working tirelessly towards the tour. In his words, “Andrews has been working very hard for this tour and I bet you, it is going to be the talk of the town for a long time in the UK. She says she would so thrill her audience that Her Royal Majesty would hear about her. UK fans should get their dancing shoes ready, save the dates and I must warn that ladies should hold on to their men because when Andrews appears with her golden voice, and sexy curves accompanied by her mind-blowing songs, it is going to be the bomb.”